{"div":{"@xmlns":"http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0","@type":"article","@xml:id":"MG-1682-09b_082","head":{"value":"[Vers sur l’illumination des galeries du Louvre.]*","id":"/div/head"},"bibl":{"title":{"value":"Mercure galant","id":"/div/bibl/title"},"#":{"value":", septembre 1682 (seconde partie) [tome 10], p. 82-86.","id":"/div/bibl/#"}},"p":{"value":"Cette Naissance a donné lieu à ces autres Vers, dont vous trouverez le tour aisé. Ils sont faits sur l’Illumination des Galeries du Louvre, &amp; le Feu tiré sur l’eau le jour de la Feste de S. Loüis.","id":"/div/p"},"quote":{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Des que le Soleil fut sous l’onde,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"La premiere Ville du monde","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Vn appareistre en un instant","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Un Palais d’un or éclatant,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Tel qu’est le Temple de la Gloire","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Peint par les Pilles de mémoire,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ou dans son pompeux appareil,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Le riche Palais du Soleil.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[7]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Une Architecture excellente,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[8]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Toute lumineuse &amp; brillante,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[9]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ravissoit par sa nouveauté,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[10]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Aussibien que par sa beauté.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[11]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"La Nuit ostant ses sombres voiles,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[12]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Montra des millions d’Etoiles,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[13]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qui n’estoient point du Firmament,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[14]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et tout parut enchantement.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[15]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Tous les Elémens sont en guerre,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[16]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Le Feu sort de l’Eau sur la Terre,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[17]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"L’Air retentit de toutes parts.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[18]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"La Paix craignit que ce fust Mars,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[19]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ou que Jupiter en colere","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[20]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Vinst foudroyer nostre Hémisphere,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[21]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Mais des Dauphins brûlans nageoient,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[22]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et d’autres en l’air voltigeoient,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[23]/#"}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qui disoient,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[24]/hi/#"}},"#":{"value":" ce n’est que la joye","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[24]/#"}},"D’un Duc que le Ciel nous envoye,","Duc par tant de vœux souhaité,","Duc qui vaut une Majesté.",{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Un Cahos d’ombre &amp; de lumiere","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[28]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Refléchissoit sur la Riviere,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[29]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Couverte de mille Bateaux,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[30]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Mais qui n’osoient troubler ses eaux,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[31]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"De peur d’effacer les Images","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[32]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qu’envoyoient tous ces beaux Rivages.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[33]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Des Jets de feu frapant les Cieux,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[34]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Surprenoient, &amp; charmoient les yeux.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[35]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"En cent figures diférentes,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[36]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"De longues flâmes ondoyantes,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[37]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Tantost calmes, tantost bruyantes,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[38]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Se mestoient au doux son des voix","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[39]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Des Trompetes &amp; des Hautbois,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[40]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Lors que la Nymphe de la Seine","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[41]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Empruntant une voix humaine,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[42]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Prononça clairement ces mots,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[43]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que repéterent les Echos.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[44]/#"}},"Nouveau Prince, dont l’origine","Toute grande, toute divine,","Vous montre tant &amp; tant de Roys","Dignes du Sceptre des François,","Plusieurs Loüis, un Charlemagne,","Un Henry, terreur de l’Espagne,","Vainqueur de ses propres Sujets,","Qui m’enrichit de ses bienfaits,","Vous sçaurez bientost leur Histoire ;","Mais pour aller droit à la gloire,","Croyez-moy, tous ces Roys si grands,","Justes, pieux, ou conquérans,","Leur bonté comme leur puissance,","Leur valeur, comme leur prudence,","Enfin tous leurs Faits inoüis,","Vous les trouverez en LOUIS.","Cessez, heureux Mortels, d’admirer ces Spéctacles,","L’Etoile de LOUIS fait bien d’autres miracles."]}}}}